'''真主穆斯林游擊隊'''（{{lang-en|Hizbul Mujahideen}}，{{lang-ar|حزب المجاھدین}}，意為「聖戰者的派對」{{sfnp|Koessling, Faith, Unity, Discipline: The ISI of Pakistan|2016|p=193}}）是在在[[印控克什米爾|印控克什米爾]]活動的[[伊斯蘭恐怖主義|伊斯蘭激進組織]]<ref>{{harvp|Staniland, Organizing Insurgency|2012}}</ref>，其目標為使克什米爾脫離[[印度|印度]]、併入[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]<ref>{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=I2avL3aZzSEC&pg=PA180 |title=Pakistan: Nationalism Without A Nation |last=Jaffrelot |first=Christophe |date=2002-05-17 |publisher=Zed Books |isbn=9781842771174 |page=180 |access-date=2021-06-20 |archive-date=2021-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323221230/https://books.google.com/books?id=I2avL3aZzSEC&pg=PA180 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{harvp|Gunaratna & Yee, Handbook of Terrorism In The Asia-Pacific|2016|p=271}}</ref>，已在印度境內發動多起襲擊<ref>{{Cite web|title=Hizbul Mujahideen takes responsibility for attack on CRPF camp|url=https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/hizbul-mujahideen-takes-responsibility-for-attack-on-crpf-camp-516091|access-date=2020-06-10|website=NDTV.com|archive-date=2020-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610194433/https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/hizbul-mujahideen-takes-responsibility-for-attack-on-crpf-camp-516091|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Refugees|first=United Nations High Commissioner for|title=Refworld {{!}} Country Reports on Terrorism 2017 - Foreign Terrorist Organizations: Hizbul Mujahideen|url=https://www.refworld.org/docid/5bcf1f4413.html|access-date=2020-06-10|website=Refworld|archive-date=2020-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200212140246/https://www.refworld.org/docid/5bcf1f4413.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Refugees|first=United Nations High Commissioner for|title=Refworld {{!}} U.S. Department of State Country Report on Human Rights Practices 1998 - India|url=https://www.refworld.org/docid/3ae6aa7d8.html|access-date=2020-06-12|website=Refworld|archive-date=2020-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200612213612/https://www.refworld.org/docid/3ae6aa7d8.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|last=Joshi|first=Manoj|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=pS5uAAAAMAAJ|title=The Lost Rebellion|date=1999-01-01|publisher=Penguin Books|isbn=978-0-14-027846-0|access-date=2021-09-19|archive-date=2016-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160617115507/https://books.google.com/books?id=pS5uAAAAMAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>，印度<ref name="MHA">{{Cite web|title=Banned Organisations|url=http://mha.nic.in/uniquepage.asp?id_pk=292|date=2013-01-29|publisher=Ministry of Home Affairs, Government of India|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130129051543/http://mha.nic.in/uniquepage.asp?id_pk=292|archive-date=2013-01-29}}
</ref>、歐盟<ref name="EU">{{Cite web|title=Council Decision (CFSP) 2015/2430 of 21 December 2015|url=http://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/HTML/?uri=CELEX:32015D2430|date=2015-12-22|publisher=Official Journal of the European Union|access-date=2017-05-15|archive-date=2019-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190110171412/https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/HTML/?uri=CELEX:32015D2430|dead-url=no}}</ref>、美國<ref name="US adds">{{cite news|date=2004-04-30|title=US adds 4 Indian outfits to terror list|newspaper=Rediff News|url=http://www.rediff.com/news/2004/apr/30us1.htm|access-date=2015-05-13|archive-date=2019-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190525030507/https://www.rediff.com/news/2004/apr/30us1.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>與加拿大<ref>{{Cite news|title=Canada labels the Proud Boys, other neo-Nazi groups as terrorists|work=CBC|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/canada-proud-boys-terrorists-1.5899186|access-date=2021-02-04|archive-date=2021-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211220015427/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/canada-proud-boys-terrorists-1.5899186|dead-url=no}}</ref>均將其視為[[恐怖組織|恐怖組織]]，巴基斯坦則認定其為合法團體{{sfnp|Kiessling|2016|p=183}}。

真主穆斯林游擊隊約於1989年由{{le|克什米尔伊斯兰联盟|Jamaat-e-Islami Kashmir}}成員{{le|穆罕默德·艾哈桑·达尔|Muhammad Ahsan Dar}}與穆罕默德·阿卜杜拉·班格魯創立<ref>{{harvp|Staniland|2014|pp=76–77}}</ref>，自成立起即受[[巴基斯坦三軍情報局|巴基斯坦三軍情報局]]（ISI）資助<ref name="Sirrs 177">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=SzGTDAAAQBAJ|title=Pakistan's Inter-Services Intelligence Directorate: Covert Action and Internal Operations|last=Sirrs|first=Owen L.|date=2016-07-01|publisher=Routledge|isbn=9781317196082|pages=177|access-date=2021-09-19|archive-date=2022-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220111113536/https://books.google.com/books?id=SzGTDAAAQBAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Kiessling 180">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=y_cgDgAAQBAJ&pg=PT180|title=Faith, Unity, Discipline: The Inter-Service-Intelligence (ISI) of Pakistan|last=Kiessling|first=Hein|date=2016-11-15|publisher=Oxford University Press|isbn=9781849048637|ref=harv|access-date=2021-09-19|archive-date=2019-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191218070243/https://books.google.com/books?id=y_cgDgAAQBAJ&pg=PT180|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{sfnp|Staniland|2014|p=80}}，游擊隊的聯絡辦事處位於巴基斯坦首都[[伊斯蘭馬巴德|伊斯蘭馬巴德]]，其總部據稱位於[[巴控克什米尔|巴控克什米尔]]的[[穆扎法拉巴德|穆扎法拉巴德]]<ref name="ceasefire aborted">{{Cite web |first1=Jaideep E. |last1=Menon |first2=Narayanan M. |last2=Komerath |url=http://www.bharat-rakshak.com/MONITOR/ISSUE3-2/narayanan.html |title=The Hizbul-Mujahideen Ceasefire Who Aborted It? BHARAT RAKSHAK MONITOR: Volume 3(2); September – October 2000 |date=2009-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090109055407/http://www.bharat-rakshak.com/MONITOR/ISSUE3-2/narayanan.html |archive-date=2009-01-09 |url-status=dead |access-date=2017-05-15 }}</ref>。有些學者將真主穆斯林游擊隊視為克什米尔伊斯兰联盟附屬的武裝團體<ref name=":18">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=qM6kW9ZRMRkC|title=Demystifying Kashmir|last1=Behera|last2=Chadha|first2=Behera Navnita|date=2007|publisher=Pearson Education India|isbn=9788131708460|pages=154|access-date=2021-09-19|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125050601/https://books.google.com/books?id=qM6kW9ZRMRkC|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{sfnp|Kiessling|2016|p=180}}。此團體是克什米爾衝突由民族主義衝突轉型成伊斯蘭激進聖戰運動的重要推手<ref>{{harvp|Garner, Chechnya and Kashmir: The Jihadist Evolution|2013|p=423}}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
1988年，當時為克什米尔伊斯兰联盟學校教師的穆罕默德·艾哈桑·达尔越境至巴控克什米尔受訓，後來回到印控克什米爾發動對印度政府的武裝抗爭，克什米尔伊斯兰联盟的另一名成員穆罕默德·阿卜杜拉·班格魯加入其組織並擔任軍事顧問，成立真主穆斯林游擊隊<ref name="rediff">{{Cite web|url=https://www.rediff.com/news/2000/jul/31hizb.htm|title=rediff.com Special: What's the Hizbul Mujahideen?|website=www.rediff.com|access-date=2019-03-20|archive-date=2020-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903202021/https://www.rediff.com/news/2000/jul/31hizb.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。組織初建之時已有超過萬名武裝成員，大部分皆在巴基斯坦受訓<ref name="ceasefire aborted"/><ref name="rediff"/>，有些則在[[阿富汗內戰|阿富汗內戰]]期間於[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]受訓<ref name=":18"/>，他們強烈譴責在屬印與屬巴之外提倡印控克什米爾獨立的其他團體，堅持克什米爾必須併入巴基斯坦<ref name="rediff"/>。

真主穆斯林游擊隊發動的第一次重大襲擊為1990年3月21日暗殺時任克什米爾{{le|米爾威茲|Mirwaiz}}與全查謨克什米爾人民行動聯盟（克什米爾的跨黨派合作聯盟）主席{{le|穆罕默德·法魯克·沙阿|Mohammad Farooq Shah}}<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.csmonitor.com/1983/0610/061054.html|title=Strategic Kashmir is divided by conflicting loyalties|date=10 June 1983|work=Christian Science Monitor|access-date=20 March 2019|issn=0882-7729|archive-date=2017-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012042331/https://m.csmonitor.com/1983/0610/061054.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/SC-upholds-life-sentence-for-killer-of-Mirwaizs-father/articleshow/6197533.cms|title=SC upholds life sentence for killer of Mirwaiz's father - Times of India|website=The Times of India|access-date=20 March 2019|archive-date=2019-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191111083102/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/SC-upholds-life-sentence-for-killer-of-Mirwaizs-father/articleshow/6197533.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，交火中共造成26人死亡<ref name="rediff"/>。

